### âœ… Example: `Single Number`

> Every number appears twice except one. Find it.

```cpp
int singleNumber(vector<int>& nums) {
    int ans = 0;
    for (int num : nums) {
        ans ^= num; // cancel duplicates
    }
    return ans;
}
```

